{
  "id": "adv_card_mna_03_02",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 2話 今は見ないで",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_coast_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-07.m4a",
      "text": "んーっ！　ライブ最高だった！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm! The live performance was amazing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-09.m4a",
      "text": "今日も頑張ったな～、私！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did my best again today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.0333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-12.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、海岸を散歩して気分転換も終わったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ I've finished my stroll along the beach for refreshing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-03.m4a",
      "text": "今日はもう帰ってぐっすり――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ I can go home and rest for today――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ライブが良かったのは確かだけど、もう一つ\n頑張るべきことを意図的に忘れようとしてないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While the live performance was great‚\nisn't there something else you should be deliberately forgetting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.1666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-02.m4a",
      "text": "残念、ごまかせなかったか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Too bad‚ you got me‚ huh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.8666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-04.m4a",
      "text": "さすが敏腕マネージャー、鋭いね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're truly a sharp manager!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.9000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なぁ、ライブを観て思ったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ I was thinking while watching the live…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2333342235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-03.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.5666675568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今回のCMで求められていることって\n麻奈にとって、そんなに難しいことなのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's required for this CM‚\nis it really that difficult for you‚ Mana?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3666675568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-05.m4a",
      "text": "それってどういう意味？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean by that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.7333342235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "歌ってる麻奈は、自然にいい表情をしているじゃないか\n恋の歌を歌ってるつもりで演技すればいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you sing‚ don't you naturally make good expressions?\nJust act as if you're singing a love song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.499998347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "今の麻奈なら、そんなに難しいことじゃないだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It shouldn't be that difficult for the current you‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.799998347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-14.m4a",
      "text": "難しいよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's difficult!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9666650136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-01.m4a",
      "text": "だって私は歌う時、演技なんてしてないもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because when I sing‚ I'm not acting or anything like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.1333324432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "歌詞の中の女の子に、なりきってるだけなんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just immerse myself in the lyrics and become the girl in the song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7999991099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "演技なんかじゃない。歌ってる間は全部本当なの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not acting. While I'm singing‚ it's all real.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.599998347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "なりきる……って、演技するより難しいんじゃないか？\n麻奈、本当にそんなこと出来るのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Immersing yourself… isn't that even harder than acting?\nCan you really do that‚ Mana?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2666624705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_surp-03.m4a",
      "text": "え？　普通は出来ないものなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Is it something that most people can't do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6666624705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "出来ないと思う。……やっぱり、麻奈は特別なんだな\nだけど、その才能はCMでは活かせないんだよな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think most people can't. …You're special after all.\nBut that talent can't be used in a CM‚ can it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.2333250682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-10.m4a",
      "text": "うん、歌ってる時限定だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it's limited to when I'm singing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2333250682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_rep-01.m4a",
      "text": "全く、全然、ちっとも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Totally‚ absolutely‚ not at all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.9999897003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-08.m4a",
      "text": "大体、私は女優さんじゃないんだよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I mean‚ I'm not an actress or anything like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.0666599274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうはっきり言われると、余計追いつめられた気分だ\n時間はないし、結構ピンチだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you put it that way‚ it makes me feel even more cornered.\nWe're running out of time‚ and it's quite a tight spot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.3666609447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-12.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんね、もっと真剣に考えておくんだった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry. I should've thought about it more seriously…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7666609447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-01.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたらいいかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should I do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.9666573843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、本命の相手を思い浮かべて\nその人にチョコを渡すつもりでやるしかない……かな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe you should just imagine your true love and\ngive them chocolates…That's the only way… maybe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.7999907177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-02.m4a",
      "text": "恥ずかしいよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's embarrassing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.8999907177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-01.m4a",
      "text": "そんな姿を全国に放送されるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To have that broadcasted nationwide…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.0333209992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-02.m4a",
      "text": "……さすが{user}くん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're something else‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.1333148957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-01.m4a",
      "text": "考えることがえげつないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your ideas are outrageous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.9999927521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……ということは、本命の相手はいるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ do you have someone special in mind?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.3333250682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
